OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fcloudier from the west overnight which
OL,7,Fmay produce some spots of rain at
OL,8,Ftimes, especially across hilly areas.
OL,9,FWinds stay light but a mild night for
OL,10,Fmany.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,13,Fweekend, and some cloud may linger
OL,14,Faround northern and western coasts.
OL,15,FElsewhere, plenty of bright and sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Light winds and feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
